Narendran is employed with Qantas Airways - Sydney, And currently he is part of their IPA CoE (Intelligent Process Automation) Advisory Group and working as an Advisor and Member Practice for RPA (Process Automation Technology) offering; 

He has 9 plus years of both Technical & Functional expertise including with Business Analysis, Process Consulting - Know-How, End to End project implementation experience focused more on Robotic Process Automation(RPA);

Previously worked with ISG/Alsbridge as a Techno Functional Consultant, Also worked with Sutherland Global Service as a Software Engineer for RPA and Tata Consultancy Services as a  Sr.Executive for RPA.

Has fair domain knowledge of Telecom, Market Research and Banking.

Adept knowledge of Software Development Life cycle (SDLC) including Requirement gathering, Analysis, Design, Development, Testing, Deployment, Delivery and Support. Posses Business Management insights with fair knowledge of Business Analysis, process analysis & discovery and Project Management and latest trends;

Certified Python  developer, Expertise in RPA tools (Blueprism, Automation Anywhere & Ui-Path)
